    "This allows us to study the flux limit at each position, based on the local background level and exposure depth.",
    "Two applications of the apetool sensitivity maps (computation of flux limits and number counts) are described in Sects. 5.4 and 5.5.",
    "SOU chainSource products (spectra, background spectra, response matrices, ancillary response files and light curves) were created using the srctool task, for the subset of bright sources with a detection likelihood greater than 20 in the single-band 1B catalogue.",
